You may have heard the word NLP used by many influential celebrities/personal development experts (e.g. Tony Robbins), successful entrepreneurs, business owners, effective coaches etc. 
WHAT IS NLP? 
NLP stands for Neuro-Linguistic Programming and in a nutshell, NLP is a modelling technology and study of HOW we do what we do, how we process information, use language to structure our thoughts, manage our state and generate effective behaviour. 
Learning the tools and techniques of NLP will equip anyone to change or enhance the way they think, feel, behave, communicate and generate results.... enhancing the quality of their life. 
I have worked with many clients who have had life changing results, regardless of their life experience, background or occupation.

If you are keen to learn how NLP can help you and are serious about Raising Your Game, review my course link and get in contact, as I'll happily answer any questions.

Who's ready for some more outstanding work from our new Chameleon Colorist team?! Today, we're joined by the talented Christian with something incredible for you all to enjoy. In this tutorial, Christian shows you some beautiful techniques for getting different tones and details into this stunning fox colouring page.
AND you'll never guess what... He's only used 8 Chameleon Pens for this entire page!

So let's hear a few words from Christian about this awesome project; "I colored the fox page from the Lori's Art Garden Poster Coloring Book, because I have this personal connection with foxes. Even if I haven't seen one in person yet, I just love how their colors blend and vary. I wanted to translate my love for the animals into this coloring page." Want to colour this gorgeous colouring page for yourself?? This page can be found in our own colouring book, which has been designed by the wonderful Lori Gardner Woods - go check it out on our website!

We're absolutely loving this stunning coloring page by Christian, but what do you want to see him create in the future? We would love it if you let us know in the comments down below. :) #chameleonpens #pen #marker #alcoholmarkers #video #tutorial #colouringpage #coloringpage #adultcolouring #adultcoloring #color #colour #colouring #coloring #colouringbook #coloringbook #tips #techniques #howto #colorist #colourist #blends #onepenblends #detail #worldofartists #artcommunity
